{{see|Logo}}
==English==
===Etymology===
Short for [[logotype]], ultimately from Ancient Greek ''logos'' meaning word or speech.

===Noun===
'''logo'''
# A [[symbol]] or [[emblem]] that acts as a [[trademark]] or a means of [[identification]] of an [[institution]] etc. Note that for an emblem to be a logo, it must contain or be derived from letters or words. Compare and contrast [[marque]] borrowed from modern French.

